  <h2 style="padding-top: 60px;">The big win</h2>
  <p>By making goals and progress visible to program managers, facility managers and health workers at the facility, health workers feel more connected to the targets. </p>
  <p>This helps foster ownership, accountability, and a stronger drive to achieve the targets set.</p>
